# Force LF for all text so generated assets are byte-stable across platforms.
# Without this, a Windows checkout (core.autocrlf=true) rewrites SVG/MD/MJS
# line endings to CRLF, and the determinism gate (local /release + CI) trips
# on phantom diffs. LF everywhere keeps `git status` clean after regen on any OS.
* text=auto eol=lf

# Binary assets git must never convert or line-ending-normalize.
*.png binary
*.ico binary
*.icns binary
